Anker Nano is a great Fast Charger for your new iPhone:

• Blazing Fast speeds (20W) - 3X faster than the original 5W iPhone charger
• Ultra Compact Size 
• Lightweight and Portable
• More affordable than the Apple Chargers in most regions
• USB-C port 

@anker_official provided us with a review unit of the Anker Nano - not a paid post

You can get Anker Nano fast Charger for your new iPhone: https://amzn.to/34bTTzE

iOS 15: Apple offers unlimited iCloud storage on iOS 15 which makes the transition process from one iPhone to another even easier than before. 

All users are now able to backup their old devices to iCloud, even if they do not have available iCloud Storage. 

This backup is available for 3 weeks which is plenty enough and serves its purpose. 

Do you appreciate this feature or do you pay for iCloud already?

Follow @9TechEleven for more Apple news.
